{"tid":2284774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"比罷交稅更好既方法","createTime":"2020-11-13T14:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T00:03:47.000Z","uid":293494,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc2eb5c3f820ead95b34f3ca199d3a12266dfee","tid":2284774,"uid":293494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:31:46.000Z","msg":"叔係減少本地消費。其實大部分連登網民入息稅絕對少過消費做成既商業稅，況且你唔交稅會上身，唔本地消費奈你唔何。<br />\n<br />\n一齊Brainstorm 下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 碌卡消費用離岸銀行/證券行既debit/credit card <br />\n2. 買股票債券基金用離岸銀行/證券行<br />\n3. MPF 轉非本地既組合<br />\n4. 網上服務（e.g., Netflix/ Facebook/ YouTube 俾錢plan） 用外國既domain<br />\n5. 上網用外國VPN，咁樣睇/㩒廣吿既分成就會去左外國既domain，出錢落廣吿就見到無人睇，就唔會再係香港地區落廣吿，本地廣吿商就無生意。<br />\n6. 用Uber 唔好call 的土<br />\n7. 最重要係賺物用外國網/水貨<br />\n8. （唔知得唔得）保險用離岸既分行<br />\n<br />\n食野避唔到，唯有去HKTVmall / 誠gor 既買，黃店食"},{"pid":"64e269b741129d09c0f455e469de80c55ecbd936","tid":2284774,"uid":34010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:37:09.000Z","msg":"Amazon <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申amazon打手"},{"pid":"982741b6ffce9e073e06424965a20f1402b1a663","tid":2284774,"uid":293494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64e269b741129d09c0f455e469de80c55ecbd936","tid":2284774,"uid":34010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:37:09.000Z","msg":"Amazon <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申amazon打手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:47:11.000Z","msg":"Thanksgiving!!! Black Friday!!!!!"},{"pid":"f644587b7bb2ec2eb8ecb45fec76974792d41695","tid":2284774,"uid":80902,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"64e269b741129d09c0f455e469de80c55ecbd936","tid":2284774,"uid":34010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:37:09.000Z","msg":"Amazon <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申amazon打手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:49:04.000Z","msg":"支持Amazon，我個個星期都上Amazon買幾百蚊野<img src=\"